query:
INSERT INTO program (id,
                                 created_date_time,
                                 modification_date_time,
                                 program_name,
                                 interval_period,
                                 program_descriptions,
                                 payload_descriptors,
                                 targets,
                                 business_id,
                                 attributes)
            VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), now(), now(), $1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7)
            RETURNING id,
                      created_date_time,
                      modification_date_time,
                      program_name,
                      interval_period,
                      program_descriptions,
                      payload_descriptors,
                      targets as  "targets:Vec<Target>",
                      attributes
